Name: ORDEAL SWITCH POSITION
checklistText:
ORDEAL SWITCH POSITION CHECK

			CAUTION
Before ORDEAL is stowed, or when
not being used (weather EARTH/
LUNAR sw is in PWR OFF or not),
FDAI 1 & 2 sw must be at INRTL.
Otherwise, pitch inertial att
cannot be displayed by FDAI ball.

Panel 13:
	FDAI sw (both) – INRTL
	EARTH/LUNAR – PWR OFF
	ALT SEL cont – as desired
	LTG – OFF
	MODE – HOLD/FAST
	SLEW – ctr
